'''小相手蟹屬'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Nanosesarma'''''}}）<ref name = "COL">{{cite web|url= http://www.catalogueoflife.org/annual-checklist/2011/search/all/key/nanosesarma/match/1|title= Species 2000 & ITIS Catalogue of Life: 2011 Annual Checklist.|author= Bisby F.A., Roskov Y.R., Orrell T.M., Nicolson D., Paglinawan L.E., Bailly N., Kirk P.M., Bourgoin T., Baillargeon G., Ouvrard D. (red.)|year= 2011|publisher= Species 2000: Reading, UK.|accessdate= 2012-09-24|language= en|archive-date= 2014-08-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140811110552/http://www.catalogueoflife.org/annual-checklist/2011/search/all/key/nanosesarma/match/1|dead-url= no}}</ref>，舊屬[[方蟹科|方蟹科]]，現從新分類作[[方蟹總科|方蟹總科]][[相手蟹科|相手蟹科]]。

本屬物種主要在[[東南亞|東南亞]]出現，計有：[[印尼|印尼]]<ref name='id12004'>{{cite web| url =http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=12004| title =小相手蟹| work =《中国动物物种编目数据库》| publisher =中国科学院微生物研究所| author =中国科学院动物研究所| accessdate =2009-04-28| archive-date =2016-03-05| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305034203/http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=12004| dead-url =yes}}</ref>的[[加里曼丹岛|加里曼丹岛]]<ref name='id12005'>{{cite web| url =http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=12005| title =刺指小相手蟹| work =《中国动物物种编目数据库》| publisher =中国科学院微生物研究所| author =中国科学院动物研究所| accessdate =2009-04-28| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305044754/http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=12005| archivedate =2016-03-05}}</ref>、[[爪哇|爪哇]]<ref name='id12006'>{{cite web| url =http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=12006| title =印尼小相手蟹| work =《中国动物物种编目数据库》| publisher =中国科学院微生物研究所| author =中国科学院动物研究所| accessdate =2009-04-28| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20131203122335/http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view| archivedate =2013-12-03}}</ref>及其他島嶼、[[马来半岛|马来半岛]]<ref name='id12005' /><ref name='id12006' />、[[新加坡|新加坡]]<ref name='id12006' />、[[泰國|泰國]]<ref name='id12004' />、[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]<ref name='id12006' />、[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]的[[海南岛|海南岛]]<ref name='id12005' /><ref name='id12006' />、[[广东|广东]]、[[福建|福建]]、[[浙江|浙江]]、[[河北|河北]]等地<ref name='id12004' />，以至印度洋的[[印度|印度]]、[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]<ref name='id12004' />及[[非洲|非洲]]大陸在印度洋沿岸的[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]、[[索馬里|索馬里]]及[[坦桑尼亞|坦桑尼亞]]亦有出沒<ref name=WoRMS_207556 >{{cite WoRMS |author=Davie, P. |year=2012 |title=Nanosesarma minutum (de Man, 1887) |id=207556  |date=2012-02-25}}</ref>。當中以[[小相手蟹|小相手蟹]]的分佈最為廣泛。

生活环境为海水，一般生活于半咸水地区红树林的泥滩沼泽中<ref name='id12006' /><ref name='id12005' />或栖息于低潮线岩石旁<ref name='id12004' />。

==物種==
本屬包含11個物種，分別如下<ref name=WoRMS_204222>{{cite WoRMS |author=Davie, P. |year=2012 |title=''Nanosesarma'' |id=204222 |accessdate=2012-12-25}}</ref>：
*''Nanosesarma andersonii'' (de Man, 1888)
*[[印尼小相手蟹|印尼小相手蟹]] ''Nanosesarma batavicum'' (Moreira, 1903)
*''Nanosesarma edamense'' (de Man, 1887)
*''Nanosesarma jousseaumei'' (Nobili, 1906)
*[[小相手蟹|小相手蟹]] ''Nanosesarma minutum'' (de Man, 1887)
*''Nanosesarma nunongi'' Tweedie, 1950
*[[刺指小相手蟹|刺指小相手蟹]] ''Nanosesarma pontianacense'' (de Man, 1895)
*''Nanosesarma sarii'' Naderloo & Türkay, 2009
*''Nanosesarma tweediei'' (Serène, 1967)
*''Nanosesarma vestitum'' (Stimpson, 1858)

WoRMS不承認[[戈氏小相手蟹|戈氏小相手蟹]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://taibif.tw/zh/catalogue_of_life/page/476d-4e66-5224-2a8c-61a1-8b5f-c9a3-c874-namecode-311123?order=solr_document&sort=desc&qt-section_quicktabs=5 |title=''Nanosesarma gordoni'' Shen, 1935 戈氏小相手蟹 |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2014-08-05 |archive-date=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811165429/http://taibif.tw/zh/catalogue_of_life/page/476d-4e66-5224-2a8c-61a1-8b5f-c9a3-c874-namecode-311123?order=solr_document&sort=desc&qt-section_quicktabs=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，認為只是小相手蟹的異名<ref name=WoRMS_455463>{{cite WoRMS |author=Davie, P. |year=2012 |title=Sesarma (Sesarma) gordoni Shen, 1935 |id=455463 |date=2012-02-25}}</ref>。

